<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Twenty-ninth session 
</b></p>
<p>Agenda item 3 
</p>
<p><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
</b></p>
<p><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights, 
</b></p>
<p><b>including the right to development 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Pakistan (on behalf of the Organization of Islamic Cooperation):* amendment to 
</b></p>
<p><b>draft resolution A/HRC/29/L.20 
</b></p>
<p><b>  29</b>/&#8230;  <b>The right to freedom of expression, including in the form of art 
</b></p>
<p>After subparagraph 3 (<i>f</i>), insert a new subparagraph <i>reading</i> 
</p>
<p>(<i>g</i>) To make the utmost effort, in accordance with their national legislation and in 
</p>
<p>conformity with international human rights and humanitarian law, to ensure that religious 
</p>
<p>places and symbols are fully respected and protected;  
</p>
<p>    
</p>
<p>  
 * With the exception of Albania and Benin. 
